title: Glen Campbell and Anne Murray (1971) MP3@320
description:
Anne Murray / Glen Campbell is an album by American singer Glen Campbell and Canadian singer Anne Murray, released in 1971 (see 1971 in music). The album contained both new material, and duet versions of songs each artist had recorded individually (Campbell's "By the Time I Get to Phoenix" and Murray's "Bring Back the Love"), as well as covers of Hank Snow's "You're Easy to Love", the standard "Canadian Sunset", and Brotherhood of Man's 1970 hit "United We Stand".

A single was released from the album, a medley of "By The Time I get to Phoenix" (sung by Campbell) and "I Say a Little Prayer" (sung by Murray).
